org.treetank.utils
Class TypedValue

java.lang.Object
  org.treetank.utils.TypedValue

public final class TypedValue
extends Object

UTF

Util to efficiently convert byte arrays to various Java types and vice versa. It also provides efficient comparison and hash methods.
